Accepted 7/16 Order on 7/19/01.  Filed Affirmative Statement on 7/27/01.
TW received bids for more than 1.3 Bcf/d of capacity.  Press release issued 9/11/01
Certificate Issued 5/7/01.  On 7/19/01 received approval to clean line.
FERC issued a Notice to proceed w/construction on 8/14/01.
Received Commission Order 7/28/00.  Updated Env. Plan filed on 7/2/01.
Firm Customer Group filed Request For Rehearing on Wheeler Ridge take-away capacity issue.
FERC issued a Draft EA finding the project to have limited adverse impact.
FERC issued a Presidential Permit to import gas.
Kern filed an answer to SWG protest arguing that SWG has not filed its alt. proposal.
Joint Notice of Intent to prepare an EIS was issued.
New meter station if 2002 -2003 expansion shippers move to Kramer Junction Del. Point from Wheeler Ridge.
Open season ended June 1.  Rec'd requests for 1 Bcf in Ph. I and l.5 Bcf in Ph. II.
Open Season ended June 19, 2001.  Rec'd binding agreements for 250MMcf/d.
